text: Kriemhild Limberg was a athlete from Germany. Limberg competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. She was born on 8 September 1934 and died on 24 August 2020.Kriemhild Limberg-Hausmann == References == Category:1934 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Discus throwers Category:Olympians for Germany
